Description: Provides functions to read 'ImageJ'
    (http://imagej.nih.gov/ij/) Region of Interest (ROI) files, to plot
    the ROIs and to convert them to 'spatstat' (http://spatstat.org/)
    spatial patterns or 'sf' spatial objects.
